Paper: hep-th/9303179

Date: 1993-03-31

Title: String Tension in QED from Coulomb Gauge Correlators

Authors: T.H. Hansson (Stockholm) and I. Zahed (Stony Brook)

Comments: Latex 3p, USITP-93-6

We discuss the new Coulomb gauge method for testing confinement and measuringthe string tension in the context of the Schwinger model and compact QED in 3dimensions.